metadata.description:
Technique

Phygital. Generated using Processing IDE, mechanically plotted with an AxiDraw v3, and photographed with a digital camera.

Media

Fine point pen, 0.2 mm, archival quality black ink on a matte white, plastic feel, elemental chlorine free, acid free, 330 gsm paper

Dimensions 

Physical: 297 x 420 mm
Digital: 3384 × 4810 px
